"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 16, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xxz1665702736293.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xxz1665702736293.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xxz1665702736293.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xxz1665702736293\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n SQLite \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xxz1665702736293__sqlite_171435\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">SQLite (SLE) is the default database provided for the Uniface Repository and is\n      appropriate for single-user use. It is not recommended for a shared Uniface\n      Repository.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"xxz1665702736293__note_x33_t1b_wcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span>\n<p class=\"p\">Version 2.0 and higher of the SLE connector cannot use databases created by the SLE U1.0\n            connector, they are incompatible. If you want to move from using SLE U1.0 to a higher\n            version of the SLE connector, you will need to export all the data from these databases\n            using the SLE U1.0 connector, and import this data into a new database created by\n            version 2.0 (SLE U2.0) or higher of the SLE connector.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n Connector Attribute/Feature\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n Mnemonic\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\">\n SLE\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n Supported Version\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\"> For the supported platforms and product versions,\n                     see the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://community.rocketsoftware.com/rocket-uniface-forum-home-20/uniface-product-availability-information-18191\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Platform Availability Matrix</a>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n Supported utilities\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\"> Create Table and Load Definitions are\n                     supported.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n SQL support\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\">\n Yes\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n Stored procedures support\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__1\">\n Database encoding\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xxz1665702736293__table_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1__entry__2\">\n UTF-8\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzu1665702542108.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DBMS Connector Overview</a><p>This section provides an overview of supported functionality and limitations for all DBMS connectors.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwm1666854365665.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Load Definitions Facility for SQLite</a><p>The Load Definitions functionality is supported for SQLite.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SQLite Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 16, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 SQLite SQLite (SLE) is the default database provided for the Uniface Repository and is appropriate for single-user use. It is not recommended for a shared Uniface Repository. CAUTION: Version 2.0 and higher of the SLE connector cannot use databases created by the SLE U1.0 connector, they are incompatible. If you want to move from using SLE U1.0 to a higher version of the SLE connector, you will need to export all the data from these databases using the SLE U1.0 connector, and import this data into a new database created by version 2.0 (SLE U2.0) or higher of the SLE connector. Connector Attribute/Feature Description Mnemonic SLE Supported Version For the supported platforms and product versions, see the Platform Availability Matrix . Supported utilities Create Table and Load Definitions are supported. SQL support Yes Stored procedures support No Database encoding UTF-8 Related Links DBMS Connector Overview This section provides an overview of supported functionality and limitations for all DBMS connectors. Load Definitions Facility for SQLite The Load Definitions functionality is supported for SQLite. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}